<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IndoBeyondBorders - Learn Indonesian Free</title>
    <meta name="description" content="IndoBeyondBorders — Free Indonesian (BIPA) courses, videos, slides and quizzes. Learn anywhere.">
    <meta property="og:title" content="IndoBeyondBorders — Learn Indonesian for Free" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Free Indonesian language courses (BIPA). Interactive lessons, videos, and downloadable resources." />
    <meta property="og:image" content="assets/image.png" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root{
            --text:#333;
            --accent1: #667eea;
            --accent2: #764ba2;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            --glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            --glass-shadow: 0 8px 36px rgba(102,126,234,0.12);
            --btn-grad: linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent1),var(--accent2));
            --logo-size: 140px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg,#f5f7ff,#eef2ff);
            -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .brand img {
            width: var(--logo-size);
            height: var(--logo-size);
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.14), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
            padding: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 70px rgba(102,126,234,0.18), 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.18) inset;
            transform: translateZ(30px) translateY(-2px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
        }

        .brand-text h1 {
            font-size: 1.6em;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        nav {
            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            justify-content:space-between;
            gap:12px;
            padding:12px 20px;
            margin: 0 20px;
            border-radius:14px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(2,6,23,0.06);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px) saturate(120%);
        }

        nav .links { display:flex; gap:18px; align-items:center; }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding:6px 10px;
            border-radius:8px;
            font-weight:700;
            transition: color 160ms ease, transform 160ms ease;
        }

        nav a:hover { color: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); }

        nav a.active{ background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), rgba(255,255,255,0.03)); }

        .disabled {
            opacity: 0.6;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Theme toggle switch */
        .theme-toggle-input { display:none; }
        .theme-switch {
            display:inline-flex;
            width:56px;
            height:30px;
            align-items:center;
            justify-content:center;
            border-radius:999px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg,#ffd86b,#ff6b6b);
            margin-right:10px;
            cursor:pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            position:relative;
            padding:4px;
        }

        .theme-switch svg { width:18px; height:18px; position:absolute; transition:opacity 180ms ease; }
        .theme-switch .moon { opacity:0; }
        .theme-toggle-input:checked + .theme-switch { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#4b6cb7,#182848); }
        .theme-toggle-input:checked + .theme-switch .moon { opacity:1; }
        .theme-toggle-input:checked + .theme-switch .sun { opacity:0; }

        .theme-switch::after{
            content:'';
            position:absolute;
            left:6px;
            width:18px;
            height:18px;
            border-radius:50%;
            background:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            transition:left 220ms cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.2,1), transform 220ms;
            box-shadow:0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        }
        .theme-toggle-input:checked + .theme-switch::after{ left:calc(100% - 24px); transform: translateX(-2px); }

        /* Theme support */
        :root[data-theme="dark"] {
            --bg: #0f1724;
            --text: #e6eef8;
        }

        :root[data-theme="dark"] body {
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(102,126,234,0.92), rgba(118,75,162,0.88));
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 110px 20px 80px 20px;
            position:relative;
            overflow:hidden;
        }

        /* dramatic subtle decor for home hero */
        .hero::before{
            content:'';
            position:absolute;
            left:-10%;
            top:-30%;
            width:60vmax;
            height:60vmax;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 20%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), transparent 30%);
            transform: rotate(14deg);
            filter: blur(28px) saturate(140%);
            opacity:0.85;
            animation: slow-rotate 18s linear infinite;
            pointer-events:none;
        }
        @keyframes slow-rotate { from{ transform: rotate(12deg) translateY(0);} to{ transform: rotate(372deg) translateY(0);} }

        /* 3D glass title box */
        .title-box {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 22px 32px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.16), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(10,20,40,0.45), inset 0 2px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            transform: perspective(900px) translateZ(36px) translateY(-6px) rotateX(0.6deg);
            transition: transform 260ms cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.2,1), box-shadow 260ms;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px) saturate(120%);
        }

        .title-box:hover { transform: perspective(900px) translateZ(60px) translateY(-12px) rotateX(1.6deg); box-shadow: 0 42px 100px rgba(10,20,40,0.55); }

        .title-box h2 { margin:0; font-size:2.4rem; letter-spacing:0.2px; color: #fff; text-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(7,18,38,0.55); }
        .title-box p { margin:6px 0 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size:1rem; }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            background: var(--btn-grad);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 34px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing:0.6px;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(102,126,234,0.18);
            transform-origin:center;
        }

        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02); box-shadow: 0 36px 86px rgba(102,126,234,0.24); }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px) saturate(120%);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px) saturate(120%);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            padding: 28px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 160ms ease, box-shadow 160ms ease;
            transform-style: preserve-3d;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(118,75,162,0.12);
        }

        /* Resource card accent for courses list */
        .resource-item {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 18px;
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
            border-radius:10px;
            padding:14px 14px 14px 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }
        .resource-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 8px;
            width: 10px;
            height: calc(100% - 16px);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg,var(--accent1),var(--accent2));
            border-radius: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(100,80,180,0.12) inset;
        }

        .resource-item p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #444;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        :root[data-theme="dark"] {
            --text:#e6eef8;
            --glass-bg: rgba(18,24,38,0.52);
            --glass-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            --glass-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(2,6,23,0.6);
            --btn-grad: linear-gradient(90deg,#334b8a,#0f1540);
        }
        :root[data-theme="dark"] .feature-card,
        :root[data-theme="dark"] .resource-item {
            color: var(--text);
            box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
        }

        
        .feature-card:hover{ transform: translateY(-12px) translateZ(6px) scale(1.01); }

  
        .btn {
            background: var(--btn-grad);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display:inline-block;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(102,126,234,0.2);
            transition: transform 180ms cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.2,1), box-shadow 180ms;
        }
        .btn:hover{ transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 28px 48px rgba(102,126,234,0.22); }

        :root[data-theme="dark"] .feature-card h3 {
            color: #9fc0ff;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        /* Modal (login) */
        .modal-overlay{ position:fixed; inset:0; background:rgba(2,6,23,0.6); display:none; align-items:center; justify-content:center; z-index:1200; }
        .modal-overlay[aria-hidden="false"]{ display:flex; }
        .modal{ width:min(540px, 92%); background:var(--glass-bg); border-radius:14px; padding:22px; box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(2,6,23,0.5); border:1px solid var(--glass-border); backdrop-filter:blur(8px); }
        .modal h3{ margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:1.2rem; }
        .modal form{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; }
        .modal input[type="text"]{ padding:12px 14px; border-radius:8px; border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); font-size:1rem; }
        .modal .modal-actions{ display:flex; gap:8px; justify-content:flex-end; margin-top:6px; }
        .modal .btn.secondary{ background:transparent; color:var(--accent1); box-shadow:none; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="brand">
            <img src="assets/image.png" alt="IndoBeyondBorders logo">
            <div class="brand-text">
                <h1>IndoBeyondBorders</h1>
                <p>Learn Indonesian Language for Free - BIPA Program</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <div class="nav-left">
            <div class="links">
                <a href="home.html">Home</a>
                <a href="courses.html" class="active">Courses</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-right" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;">
            <input id="themeToggle" class="theme-toggle-input" type="checkbox" />
            <label for="themeToggle" class="theme-switch" title="Toggle theme">
                <svg class="sun" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4" fill="#FFD54A"/><g stroke="#FFD54A" stroke-width="1.2"><path d="M12 2v2"/><path d="M12 20v2"/><path d="M4.2 4.2l1.4 1.4"/><path d="M18.4 18.4l1.4 1.4"/><path d="M2 12h2"/><path d="M20 12h2"/><path d="M4.2 19.8l1.4-1.4"/><path d="M18.4 5.6l1.4-1.4"/></g></svg>
                <svg class="moon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1111.21 3 7 7 0 0021 12.79z" fill="#FFF" opacity="0.95"/></svg>
            </label>
            <span id="userDisplay" style="color:white; margin-right:8px; font-weight:600;"></span>
            <button id="loginBtn" class="btn">Login</button>
            <button id="logoutBtn" class="btn" style="display:none">Logout</button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="title-box reveal">
            <h2>Materials & Interactive Lessons</h2>
            <p>Structured courses, videos and hands-on practice for all levels.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:18px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:12px;">
            <a href="#features" class="btn cta-pulse reveal">Explore Materials</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="features">
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>Materials</h3>
                <p>Comprehensive learning materials covering grammar, vocabulary, and cultural insights.</p>

                <div class="resource-list">
                    <div class="resource-item">
                        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;">Slides</h4>
                        <p>Downloadable slide decks with clear summaries, examples, and suggested exercises.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="resource-item">
                        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;">Videos</h4>
                        <p>Short lessons and recorded lectures with captions and timestamps for quick review.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="resource-item">
                        <h4 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;">Quizzes</h4>
                        <p>Interactive quizzes that give instant feedback and explanations for each answer.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>Preview</h3>
                <p>Sample slides and a practice quiz will be available here. No buttons — just sample cards when ready.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 IndoBeyondBorders. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
    <!-- Login modal -->
    <div id="loginModal" class="modal-overlay" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true" aria-labelledby="loginTitle">
        <div class="modal" role="document">
            <h3 id="loginTitle">Sign in to IndoBeyondBorders</h3>
            <form id="loginForm">
                <label for="loginName">Full name</label>
                <input id="loginName" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" required />
                <div class="modal-actions">
                    <button type="button" id="loginCancel" class="btn secondary">Cancel</button>
                    <button type="submit" id="loginSubmit" class="btn">Sign in</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="assets/app.js"></script>
</body>

</html>